WEBVTT

00:00:03.350 --> 00:00:04.350
You...

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:05.840
Have you been inside my house?

00:00:06.650 --> 00:00:07.660
What?

00:00:08.910 --> 00:00:09.990
Why are you asking me that?

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:27.240
Fuu...

00:00:31.010 --> 00:00:32.119
Fuu, listen to me.

00:00:32.120 --> 00:00:35.260
Sara senpai, I'm the one
asking the questions now.

00:00:45.570 --> 00:00:46.570
Okay...

00:00:49.250 --> 00:00:50.730
Are you really from a parallel world?

00:00:52.730 --> 00:00:54.410
Just give me a straight answer. Yes or no.

00:00:57.660 --> 00:00:58.660
No.

00:00:59.820 --> 00:01:00.820
So everything...

00:01:02.770 --> 00:01:04.440
Even the fact that we were together...

00:01:05.630 --> 00:01:06.630
Was it all just a lie?

00:01:15.340 --> 00:01:16.340
I'm so sorry...

00:01:22.690 --> 00:01:23.690
Wait.

00:01:23.810 --> 00:01:24.920
- Let me explain.
- No.

00:01:26.540 --> 00:01:27.740
Just let me finish.

00:01:28.100 --> 00:01:30.300
- When I woke up back then...
- I don't want to hear it!

00:01:30.570 --> 00:01:31.570
Let go of me!

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:35.900
Didn't you say you loved me?

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:39.830
If you actually meant it,

00:01:39.880 --> 00:01:41.080
then let me go right now.

00:01:49.100 --> 00:01:50.250
I messed up.

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:34.200
"The Boy Next World My Destiny"
(Episode 10)

00:03:25.220 --> 00:03:27.510
Man, what are we supposed to do now?

00:03:27.770 --> 00:03:28.770
Whoa!

00:03:30.390 --> 00:03:31.390
What's your problem?

00:03:31.580 --> 00:03:32.580
Nothing...

00:03:33.046 --> 00:03:35.166
I used to always hear you
coming before you got here.

00:03:36.900 --> 00:03:38.970
Wait, what were you
saying about what to do?

00:03:39.350 --> 00:03:40.350
Oh, right.

00:03:41.330 --> 00:03:42.530
About Sara and Fuu.

00:03:45.370 --> 00:03:46.530
I saw Fuu this morning.

00:03:47.320 --> 00:03:48.560
He said he knows the truth now.

00:03:49.750 --> 00:03:50.750
Fuu said that himself?

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:52.280
No way.

00:03:53.126 --> 00:03:55.046
Fuu would never talk bad
about someone he likes.

00:03:55.990 --> 00:03:57.240
Even if he was being tricked...

00:03:58.320 --> 00:03:59.960
Even if it wasn't exactly "being tricked."

00:04:04.300 --> 00:04:05.500
Do you know something?

00:04:06.190 --> 00:04:07.390
Do you believe me?

00:04:09.660 --> 00:04:11.710
About that mind-reading thing?

00:04:12.870 --> 00:04:13.870
Well...

00:04:14.050 --> 00:04:15.050
To be precise,

00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:16.780
I can hear people's thoughts.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:20.000
But I've kept it a secret.
Even Fuu doesn't know.

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:21.720
Why?

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:24.400
People would just think I'm crazy.

00:04:25.290 --> 00:04:27.410
They'd either call me a liar
or some attention seeker.

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:30.400
And even if they did believe
me, they'd just be scared of me.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:32.730
Then why are you telling me?

00:04:38.900 --> 00:04:39.900
Because I like you.

00:04:41.580 --> 00:04:42.820
I want to be fair with you.

00:04:43.900 --> 00:04:45.000
Now that I've said it,

00:04:45.174 --> 00:04:46.730
you have every right to walk away.

00:04:47.140 --> 00:04:47.760
Walk away?

00:04:47.761 --> 00:04:49.499
I mean, it's pretty creepy being
able to hear thoughts, right?

00:04:49.500 --> 00:04:50.620
Why would I care about that?

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:02.900
Is it because I don't need
to hear them, so I can't?

00:05:03.420 --> 00:05:05.540
You really wear your heart
on your sleeve, don't you?

00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:19.650
When it comes to how you feel,

00:05:20.810 --> 00:05:23.330
I don't want to just listen in. I
want you to tell me yourself.

00:05:25.630 --> 00:05:26.830
How do you feel about me?

00:05:27.470 --> 00:05:28.790
Do you like me even a little bit?

00:05:39.540 --> 00:05:40.780
You first.

00:05:43.690 --> 00:05:44.890
I already said it.

00:05:45.470 --> 00:05:46.710
I didn't hear you.

00:05:50.110 --> 00:05:51.310
Taiga senpai.

00:05:53.210 --> 00:05:54.210
I like you.

00:05:57.010 --> 00:05:58.270
I really, really like you.

00:06:03.100 --> 00:06:04.660
Not knowing what someone is thinking...

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:07.080
It's actually pretty terrifying.

00:06:12.050 --> 00:06:13.500
Even if you can hear me,

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.920
I'm not going anywhere.

00:06:19.260 --> 00:06:20.460
Even if...

00:06:21.290 --> 00:06:22.490
I'm the one you've fallen for.

00:06:58.600 --> 00:06:59.600
Here.

00:07:00.120 --> 00:07:01.276
They said it's going
to rain this afternoon.

00:07:01.300 --> 00:07:04.000
(Thanks.)

00:07:13.750 --> 00:07:14.750
Thanks.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:03.500
(Thanks.)

00:08:07.460 --> 00:08:09.020
I'm not going to hide anything anymore.

00:08:09.820 --> 00:08:10.820
All of it...

00:08:11.410 --> 00:08:12.610
It was all me.

00:08:25.750 --> 00:08:26.290
Shut up.

00:08:26.290 --> 00:08:26.760
You're always like this.

00:08:26.761 --> 00:08:28.361
What about me? Why didn't you invite me?

00:08:28.390 --> 00:08:30.489
- But the vibe was great.
- You call that great?

00:08:30.490 --> 00:08:33.130
Hey, you're acting like it doesn't even
matter if I'm there or not!

00:08:36.540 --> 00:08:37.540
Morning.

00:08:38.140 --> 00:08:38.650
Morning.

00:08:39.090 --> 00:08:40.390
Good morning.

00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:49.100
Go give this to him.

00:08:49.140 --> 00:08:50.930
Huh? Me?

00:08:51.020 --> 00:08:52.850
You're the one who caused this mess, right?

00:08:53.140 --> 00:08:54.140
Well...

00:08:54.540 --> 00:08:55.450
Hurry up.

00:08:55.470 --> 00:08:56.040
Ugh...

00:08:56.041 --> 00:08:57.640
Go on, give it to him.

00:09:03.520 --> 00:09:04.520
Fuu.

00:09:09.814 --> 00:09:10.830
Here.

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:34.500
(Eat something. We're worried about you.)

00:09:44.260 --> 00:09:45.620
Everyone's worried.

00:09:48.070 --> 00:09:49.790
But he's the one who's most worried of all.

00:09:51.260 --> 00:09:52.460
You two should really talk.

00:10:17.830 --> 00:10:19.450
There was no guardian angel.

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:25.960
It had nothing to do with lucky charms.

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:33.160
It was all Sara senpai...

00:11:33.790 --> 00:11:34.800
Fuu.

00:11:36.470 --> 00:11:38.850
I think you know I'm
not very good with words.

00:11:39.250 --> 00:11:41.340
I don't even know if
you'll ever see this video.

00:11:45.230 --> 00:11:46.830
I'll probably say the wrong thing.

00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:51.280
I might even make you angrier.

00:11:53.470 --> 00:11:57.250
I know I'm a hopeless liar...

00:11:57.810 --> 00:11:58.850
But there's just one thing

00:11:59.870 --> 00:12:01.590
I need you to believe.

00:12:05.410 --> 00:12:06.610
I love you.

00:12:08.530 --> 00:12:13.550
I have since high school.
It's always been you.

00:12:21.650 --> 00:12:22.950
I'll never forget

00:12:24.900 --> 00:12:28.940
how you saved my life.

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.240
Knock, knock, knock.

00:12:31.640 --> 00:12:32.640
Who is it?

00:12:35.100 --> 00:12:36.330
Before that,

00:12:36.780 --> 00:12:38.249
my life was just a tool
for my mother's revenge.

00:12:38.250 --> 00:12:39.750
I had no freedom.

00:12:43.390 --> 00:12:45.110
People just saw what they wanted to see,

00:12:47.050 --> 00:12:48.450
projecting their fantasies onto me,

00:12:49.260 --> 00:12:50.360
or just being jealous.

00:12:51.930 --> 00:12:53.639
That's the kind of talk that pisses me off.

00:12:53.640 --> 00:12:54.640
Huh?

00:12:54.690 --> 00:12:56.640
Maybe he's actually working hard, you know?

00:12:57.100 --> 00:12:59.090
You don't know anything,
so stop talking trash.

00:13:01.760 --> 00:13:03.010
But you...

00:13:04.180 --> 00:13:05.570
you were the only
one who was different.

00:13:07.490 --> 00:13:09.290
It was the first time
I'd ever felt that way.

00:13:17.770 --> 00:13:19.490
That feeling of wanting to cherish someone.

00:13:20.140 --> 00:13:21.370
I finally understood.

00:13:23.550 --> 00:13:27.560
From then on, I just watched
over you from the shadows.

00:13:28.810 --> 00:13:30.540
Oh, thanks.

00:13:30.640 --> 00:13:31.840
Excuse me.

00:13:32.750 --> 00:13:36.000
Fuu, do you already have a college in mind?

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:38.980
Yeah, I want to go to
the same one my dad did.

00:13:39.180 --> 00:13:40.180
The university,

00:13:40.377 --> 00:13:41.537
this apartment building...

00:13:42.486 --> 00:13:43.826
I chose them all because of you.

00:13:44.020 --> 00:13:47.100
My place is right below yours.

00:13:48.050 --> 00:13:49.250
I just wanted to see your face

00:13:52.490 --> 00:13:54.070
every single day.

00:14:00.630 --> 00:14:02.950
It was the only thing that kept me going.

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:07.660
I'm sorry. I know I
sound like a total creep.

00:14:08.420 --> 00:14:09.620
But I really...

00:14:10.020 --> 00:14:11.680
I never expected anything more.

00:14:12.700 --> 00:14:15.150
Until that rainy night when I almost died.

00:14:17.300 --> 00:14:18.610
My only regret was

00:14:20.520 --> 00:14:22.840
that I never got the
chance to actually know you.

00:14:26.430 --> 00:14:27.530
Not even once.

00:14:30.640 --> 00:14:32.119
Even so, it was because of you

00:14:32.120 --> 00:14:33.500
that I wanted to keep living.

00:14:35.840 --> 00:14:36.840
Fuu,

00:14:38.550 --> 00:14:40.030
you are my whole life.

00:14:50.270 --> 00:14:52.350
I really do love you.

00:14:56.890 --> 00:14:58.270
You don't have to forgive me.

00:14:59.470 --> 00:15:00.470
Everything...

00:15:02.170 --> 00:15:03.610
It's all my fault.

00:15:08.690 --> 00:15:09.890
Enough...

00:15:11.900 --> 00:15:13.390
Stop it...

00:15:22.850 --> 00:15:24.050
I promise you,

00:15:27.340 --> 00:15:28.340
I will never

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:31.720
show my face to you again.

00:15:32.740 --> 00:15:33.840
Sara senpai?

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:37.360
No...

00:15:37.433 --> 00:15:38.433
If you can...

00:15:39.790 --> 00:15:41.540
- Come back to me.
- Fuu.

00:15:42.850 --> 00:15:44.320
Don't leave me behind.

00:15:46.580 --> 00:15:48.410
Let me keep watching over you, okay?

00:16:01.320 --> 00:16:02.320
Don't go...

00:16:05.630 --> 00:16:07.070
I'm sorry, it's all my fault...

00:16:25.930 --> 00:16:27.130
Adachi! Adachi!

00:16:27.940 --> 00:16:29.060
Have you seen Sara senpai?

00:16:29.500 --> 00:16:31.290
No, I haven't.

00:16:33.840 --> 00:16:35.629
Fuu, what's wrong?

00:16:35.630 --> 00:16:36.960
Sara senpai...

00:16:37.370 --> 00:16:40.309
Oh, I just saw Taiga senpai.

00:16:40.310 --> 00:16:41.310
Where?

00:16:42.219 --> 00:16:43.419
He went that way.

00:16:46.323 --> 00:16:47.523
Taiga senpai!

00:16:49.330 --> 00:16:50.360
Where's Sara senpai?

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:53.470
Oh.

00:16:55.030 --> 00:16:56.040
Sara...

00:16:58.763 --> 00:17:00.043
He went back to his family home.

00:17:00.290 --> 00:17:02.300
This pan-seared fish is delicious.

00:17:02.550 --> 00:17:04.100
I love pan-seared fish too.

00:17:04.840 --> 00:17:06.309
We really are a perfect match.

00:17:06.310 --> 00:17:07.340
Yeah.

00:17:14.100 --> 00:17:15.850
Are you feeling okay?

00:17:16.580 --> 00:17:17.580
Just eat.

00:17:22.070 --> 00:17:23.620
I'm not here for a family reunion.

00:17:25.050 --> 00:17:26.130
Let's get down to business.

00:17:30.530 --> 00:17:33.080
You'll start working at our
company after graduation.

00:17:33.770 --> 00:17:35.650
And we'll have the
wedding wrapped up by April.

00:17:36.820 --> 00:17:38.760
Everything has been arranged.

00:17:38.940 --> 00:17:41.430
Thank you, ma'am.

00:17:43.410 --> 00:17:45.820
Sara, where are you going?

00:17:45.830 --> 00:17:47.210
I understand perfectly.

00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:51.050
My life after graduation is
yours to do with as you please.

00:17:53.130 --> 00:17:56.030
That's my boy.

00:18:12.300 --> 00:18:13.500
Hey, what are you doing?

00:18:15.570 --> 00:18:17.480
Stop! Get back here!

00:18:45.570 --> 00:18:46.570
Fuu!

00:18:46.770 --> 00:18:47.770
Sara senpai!

00:18:49.240 --> 00:18:50.400
Fuu, what are you doing here?

00:18:51.070 --> 00:18:52.400
You little brat!

00:18:53.230 --> 00:18:54.710
Let's run away together, Sara senpai!

00:18:54.850 --> 00:18:56.400
Fuu, not that way! This way!

00:18:57.600 --> 00:18:58.830
Don't let them get away!

00:19:02.500 --> 00:19:05.000
Oh, is it that way?

00:19:05.430 --> 00:19:06.430
Fuu.

00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:11.440
Um...

00:19:20.600 --> 00:19:21.600
Sara senpai.

00:19:22.730 --> 00:19:24.370
Are you planning on breaking up with Fuu?

00:19:33.290 --> 00:19:34.490
Let me rephrase that.

00:19:35.670 --> 00:19:37.230
Do you still intend to keep loving me?

00:19:41.200 --> 00:19:42.200
Of course.

00:19:42.530 --> 00:19:43.730
There's no other answer.

00:19:45.610 --> 00:19:47.490
Game over.

00:19:51.870 --> 00:19:54.400
Found them! Grab them!

00:19:56.180 --> 00:19:57.680
Fuu, run!

00:19:58.900 --> 00:20:00.140
- Stay still!
- Fuu!

00:20:00.910 --> 00:20:02.120
Let go of him!

00:20:03.020 --> 00:20:04.020
Sara senpai.

00:20:04.103 --> 00:20:06.293
Tell your mother and your
fiancée the truth about us.

00:20:09.180 --> 00:20:10.180
Fuu and I...

00:20:11.470 --> 00:20:13.050
We're together.

00:20:14.160 --> 00:20:15.390
We're in love.

00:20:18.000 --> 00:20:19.000
Love?

00:20:20.570 --> 00:20:22.170
That's a useless emotion.

00:20:22.350 --> 00:20:23.720
You have no need for it.

00:20:26.670 --> 00:20:28.440
That's why I never gave you any.

00:20:30.420 --> 00:20:31.520
Even so,

00:20:32.370 --> 00:20:33.836
do you even consider yourself a mother?

00:20:33.860 --> 00:20:34.860
Exactly.

00:20:35.330 --> 00:20:36.750
I'm the owner.

00:20:37.340 --> 00:20:40.550
Sara is nothing more than an asset to me.

00:20:42.100 --> 00:20:44.480
Haven't you used him long enough?

00:20:45.710 --> 00:20:46.710
Soshi?

00:20:47.350 --> 00:20:48.810
What are you doing here?

00:20:50.730 --> 00:20:53.040
I'm surprised you even remember my name.

00:20:53.520 --> 00:20:54.640
I'm the one who called him.

00:20:55.970 --> 00:20:57.870
To finish the final step of this plan.

00:20:58.140 --> 00:20:59.960
Everything is going exactly as intended.

00:21:01.580 --> 00:21:03.480
I won't let a monster
like you get your way.

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:05.839
What on earth

00:21:05.840 --> 00:21:06.840
are you two talking about?

00:21:06.841 --> 00:21:08.890
Soshi and I pooled our resources

00:21:10.223 --> 00:21:11.913
and bought up the company's shares.

00:21:15.490 --> 00:21:17.020
So you two brothers

00:21:17.150 --> 00:21:18.590
are playing at some revenge fantasy?

00:21:19.210 --> 00:21:20.720
Don't make me laugh.

00:21:21.780 --> 00:21:23.470
What could a couple of children

00:21:23.820 --> 00:21:25.290
possibly achieve?

00:21:33.740 --> 00:21:34.740
Hello?

00:21:36.480 --> 00:21:37.480
Yes.

00:21:38.100 --> 00:21:39.100
I see.

00:21:42.230 --> 00:21:43.230
Understood.

00:21:44.590 --> 00:21:45.810
Thank you.

00:21:47.640 --> 00:21:48.840
Dad.

00:21:54.170 --> 00:21:56.930
You've treated this company like
your personal property for too long.

00:21:58.780 --> 00:22:00.750
The employees were fed up.

00:22:01.880 --> 00:22:04.280
Dad's been keeping in touch
with them since he retired.

00:22:05.980 --> 00:22:08.290
Thanks to him, we were able
to set everything in motion.

00:22:09.380 --> 00:22:11.740
And just now, the board of directors...

00:22:13.620 --> 00:22:16.470
Officially voted to remove
you as chairperson.

00:22:20.670 --> 00:22:21.670
Removed...?

00:22:22.590 --> 00:22:23.790
Me?

00:22:24.190 --> 00:22:25.910
Your time is over.

00:22:27.780 --> 00:22:29.690
No one is going to follow
your orders anymore.

00:22:32.010 --> 00:22:33.110
Ganbara!

00:22:42.470 --> 00:22:43.470
I understand.

00:22:46.830 --> 00:22:47.840
I'm afraid

00:22:48.290 --> 00:22:50.410
you are no longer my employer.

00:22:53.580 --> 00:22:54.580
Let's go.

00:22:55.280 --> 00:22:56.610
Even you...

00:22:57.000 --> 00:22:58.000
This has to be a joke!

00:22:59.090 --> 00:23:02.040
What about my glorious future?

00:23:02.470 --> 00:23:04.000
The only future I care about

00:23:07.150 --> 00:23:09.070
is the one with the person I love.

00:23:11.400 --> 00:23:12.640
I don't need anything else.

00:23:15.900 --> 00:23:17.000
Goodbye.

00:23:18.220 --> 00:23:19.220
Mom.

00:23:48.060 --> 00:23:49.060
You know,

00:23:49.710 --> 00:23:52.566
I really thought I was just a replacement
for the Fuu in the parallel world.

00:23:52.590 --> 00:23:54.080
That's why I kept telling myself

00:23:54.150 --> 00:23:56.130
that I couldn't let
myself truly fall for you.

00:23:58.590 --> 00:23:59.590
Now,

00:24:00.030 --> 00:24:02.110
part of me is relieved it was all a lie,

00:24:03.170 --> 00:24:05.640
but another part wonders if everything
I loved was a lie too.

00:24:09.170 --> 00:24:10.170
It wasn't a lie.

00:24:12.220 --> 00:24:14.220
I'm sorry I made it so
hard for you to believe me.

00:24:16.350 --> 00:24:17.570
But I truly...

00:24:23.970 --> 00:24:25.530
Is Fuu what makes you happy, Sara senpai?

00:24:29.860 --> 00:24:31.500
Fuu makes me happy.

00:24:34.990 --> 00:24:35.990
In that case,

00:24:36.500 --> 00:24:38.380
you'll be happy forever.

00:24:40.500 --> 00:24:41.600
Sara senpai.

00:24:41.660 --> 00:24:43.150
You deserve to be happy.

00:24:50.580 --> 00:24:51.630
Thank you.

00:24:52.800 --> 00:24:53.800
Fuu.

00:26:05.030 --> 00:26:06.130
Sara senpai.

00:26:06.720 --> 00:26:07.820
Hurry up!

00:27:34.340 --> 00:27:35.340
Are you okay?

00:27:38.000 --> 00:27:39.200
What do you mean?

00:27:43.690 --> 00:27:44.990
I should be asking you.

00:27:45.580 --> 00:27:47.740
Don't you get tired of taking
care of me all the time?

00:27:50.910 --> 00:27:52.340
I do it because I want to.

00:27:54.800 --> 00:27:57.120
Though I guess I might
have overdone it sometimes.

00:28:08.010 --> 00:28:09.950
Like knowing exactly what I want to eat,

00:28:10.770 --> 00:28:12.530
or finding things I've lost?

00:28:17.190 --> 00:28:19.270
You like bread and root
vegetables for breakfast.

00:28:20.930 --> 00:28:23.520
You always stuff things
in your back pocket.

00:28:28.300 --> 00:28:30.140
You always forget your
umbrella when it rains.

00:28:32.160 --> 00:28:34.420
You love the special curry
bread from the cafeteria.

00:28:37.300 --> 00:28:39.500
And those "lucky" boxers?

00:28:41.890 --> 00:28:43.570
They actually just fell from your balcony.

00:28:44.290 --> 00:28:45.290
Are you serious?

00:28:45.690 --> 00:28:46.690
Yeah.

00:28:49.060 --> 00:28:51.580
I thought I'd just been
on a lucky streak for years.

00:28:54.010 --> 00:28:56.090
I had no idea it was all you.

00:28:58.220 --> 00:28:59.220
I'm sorry.

00:28:59.270 --> 00:29:00.650
I should have realized sooner.

00:29:09.590 --> 00:29:11.280
It's my fault for being so insecure.

00:29:13.790 --> 00:29:15.550
That's why I made
everything so complicated.

00:29:22.480 --> 00:29:23.770
But back then,

00:29:25.680 --> 00:29:27.940
the scar really did disappear.

00:29:29.020 --> 00:29:30.020
I didn't just imagine it.

00:29:31.720 --> 00:29:33.640
And you really did seem
like a different person.

00:29:38.190 --> 00:29:40.160
I'm not from a parallel world.

00:29:41.750 --> 00:29:42.750
But...

00:29:43.530 --> 00:29:46.250
If I told you they really did exist,

00:29:48.670 --> 00:29:50.030
would you believe me?

00:30:02.160 --> 00:30:03.520
Can you read my mind?

00:30:03.990 --> 00:30:04.990
No.

00:30:07.230 --> 00:30:08.610
Then just ask me.

00:30:10.310 --> 00:30:11.310
Okay.

00:30:12.590 --> 00:30:13.980
What are you thinking right now?

00:30:21.790 --> 00:30:22.790
I love you.

00:30:23.120 --> 00:30:24.120
What?

00:30:25.280 --> 00:30:28.030
I think I've really fallen for you.

00:30:28.600 --> 00:30:29.600
Hmm?

00:30:31.113 --> 00:30:32.993
I thought it was impossible,

00:30:33.920 --> 00:30:36.200
but I'm getting more and more...

00:30:38.170 --> 00:30:40.010
I guess I'm more
simple-minded than I thought.

00:30:47.130 --> 00:30:48.130
Senpai.

00:30:50.270 --> 00:30:51.470
Can I pursue you?

00:30:52.530 --> 00:30:53.530
Yeah.

00:30:56.540 --> 00:30:57.740
Be my boyfriend?

00:31:00.370 --> 00:31:01.370
Yeah.

00:31:02.140 --> 00:31:03.340
Do you love me?

00:31:05.610 --> 00:31:06.610
Yeah.

00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:11.290
I'm so happy.

00:31:12.710 --> 00:31:14.750
It's like I can actually
hear what's in your heart.

00:31:29.790 --> 00:31:30.790
Sara senpai.

00:31:43.860 --> 00:31:44.860
Here.

00:31:53.900 --> 00:31:55.000
You said it before, right?

00:31:55.880 --> 00:31:57.560
That if you could turn back time,

00:31:57.900 --> 00:31:59.100
you would have answered me.

00:32:12.380 --> 00:32:13.380
Knock, knock, knock.

00:32:13.990 --> 00:32:14.990
Who is it?

00:32:15.910 --> 00:32:17.300
Fuu calling Sara senpai.

00:32:17.510 --> 00:32:18.510
Can you hear me?

00:32:25.590 --> 00:32:27.360
It's Sara, and I'm in love with you.

00:32:32.800 --> 00:32:33.800
Really?

00:32:36.060 --> 00:32:38.050
I wasted so many years.

00:32:40.920 --> 00:32:41.920
From now on,

00:32:42.500 --> 00:32:44.780
I won't waste another second.

00:32:46.050 --> 00:32:47.450
I love you.

00:33:18.670 --> 00:33:20.510
No matter what world we're in,

00:33:22.210 --> 00:33:24.010
there's only one Fuu for me.

00:33:28.860 --> 00:33:32.370
And no matter which
Sara senpai comes along,

00:33:33.350 --> 00:33:36.030
you're the only one I'll ever love.

00:33:37.190 --> 00:33:38.290
You trust me?

00:33:39.910 --> 00:33:41.010
You have to trust me too.

00:33:44.500 --> 00:33:45.500
Of course.

00:33:51.960 --> 00:33:53.960
Come here, you big baby.

00:34:08.120 --> 00:34:09.120
I love you.

00:34:10.340 --> 00:34:11.340
I love you too.